points.title: You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and for the activities on your account
points.quoteText: If you create an account on the Website, you are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and you are fully responsible for all activities that occur under the account and any other actions taken in connection with it.

User content

We do not own any data, information or material ("Content") that you submit on the Website in the course of using the Service

points.title: The service collects many different types of personal data
points.quoteText: When you register for an Account, we may ask for your contact information, including items such as name, company name, address, email address, and telephone number.
